  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 6 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "So far 6 million people have not received Covid vaccines - Ministry of Health",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "6 million people above the age of 20 in the country have not yet received the corona vaccines.",
        "Therefore, those who have not received the vaccine properly so far should get it quickly, said Samitha Kinike, a specialist in infectious diseases department of the Ministry of Health.",
        "More than 6 million people above the age of 20 have not received booster vaccinations in the country so far.",
        "It is essential for people to get booster shots to protect themselves from Covid infection.",
        "More and more covid infections are now being identified. So we urge you to get vaccinated as soon as possible.",
        "There is no shortage of vaccines in the country. He said vaccinations can be obtained from Health Medical Officer units and hospitals."
      ],
